CLEANING DATASET 8

Removing unwanted columns and changing the data type for a couple of columns.

STEP 1- Click Transfer data

STEP 2- Right click on the column name and change the data type 

STEP 3- By clicking control select unwanted column

STEP 4- Click Removing Colum

STEP 5- Close and apply
